update their icons by June 24.

00:30:32.152 --> 00:30:33.860
The goal here is really
to provide a more

00:30:33.860 --> 00:30:35.510
clean and polished
user experience

00:30:35.510 --> 00:30:38.090
within the store for our users.

00:30:38.090 --> 00:30:40.610
For those of you who can't
