00:30:43.760 --> 00:30:46.175
until you have time
to update them.

00:30:46.175 --> 00:30:48.050
OK, with that let's
switch gears a little bit

00:30:48.050 --> 00:30:51.050
and talk about games discovery.

00:30:51.050 --> 00:30:53.870
So I thought it'd be interesting
to give a little bit of context

00:30:53.870 --> 00:30:56.833
as we've been thinking about
this space for a long time.

00:30:56.833 --> 00:30:58.250
We had two key
insights that we're

00:30:58.250 --> 00:31:00.000
thinking about how to
evolve the discovery

00:31:00.000 --> 00:31:01.740
experience in the store.

00:31:01.740 --> 00:31:05.270
First, we realized that most
of the discovery experience

00:31:05.270 --> 00:31:08.270
is centered around a single
piece of metadata, your app

00:31:08.270 --> 00:31:09.267
icon.

00:31:09.267 --> 00:31:11.600
And while you all spend a lot
of time thinking about how

00:31:11.600 --> 00:31:14.930
to tune that icon to communicate
your brand, the IP of the game,

00:31:14.930 --> 00:31:17.160
the category, et cetera,
at the end of the day,

00:31:17.160 --> 00:31:19.077
there's a physical limit
with how much you can

00:31:19.077 --> 00:31:21.320
communicate with those pixels.

00:31:21.320 --> 00:31:22.970
The second
realization we had was

00:31:22.970 --> 00:31:24.950
that the deeper you go
into the user funnel,

00:31:24.950 --> 00:31:27.380
the closer you get the user
to the actual experience

00:31:27.380 --> 00:31:28.465
of playing the game.

00:31:28.465 --> 00:31:29.840
The more compelling
and rich that

00:31:29.840 --> 00:31:34.800
content is enabling users
to make informed choices.

00:31:34.800 --> 00:31:36.800
And as a result, we
really tried to push

00:31:36.800 --> 00:31:39.740
for a more content forward
experience in the Play Store.

00:31:39.740 --> 00:31:41.600
Drawing all of that
great rich content

00:31:41.600 --> 00:31:43.370
from the game, your
store listings page,

00:31:43.370 --> 00:31:46.313
and syndicating it
all across the store.

00:31:46.313 --> 00:31:48.230
And you can see examples
of this in production

00:31:48.230 --> 00:31:51.140
today with things like trailers
and screenshots, auto playing

00:31:51.140 --> 00:31:52.700
videos, and events.

00:31:52.700 --> 00:31:55.730
These formats are a great
way to attract new users

00:31:55.730 --> 00:31:57.420
and to be eligible for them.

00:31:57.420 --> 00:32:01.170
You just need to make sure
that you've done two things.

00:32:01.170 --> 00:32:03.950
First, you need to make sure
that you have at least three 16

00:32:03.950 --> 00:32:07.250
by 9 screenshots uploaded
to the developer console.

00:32:07.250 --> 00:32:10.280
And second, you need to check
that your promotional video

00:32:10.280 --> 00:32:15.500
has monetization disabled
and is made public.

00:32:15.500 --> 00:32:18.890
We also launched Google
Play Instant last year

00:32:18.890 --> 00:32:21.985
with the goal of furthering
this content forward experience.

00:32:21.985 --> 00:32:23.360
The goal here is
really to enable

00:32:23.360 --> 00:32:26.300
users to jump in and
try the game out,

00:32:26.300 --> 00:32:28.520
getting a quick feel for
it without having to commit

00:32:28.520 --> 00:32:31.100
to installing or uninstalling.

00:32:31.100 --> 00:32:33.260
And we've seen massive
growth in the adoption

00:32:33.260 --> 00:32:35.460
of instant, especially
amongst our largest,

00:32:35.460 --> 00:32:38.730
most successful partners
in the ecosystem.

00:32:38.730 --> 00:32:41.030
The number of instant
games has exploded--

00:32:41.030 --> 00:32:43.850
hundreds of them in the
store actually and developers

00:32:43.850 --> 00:32:47.150
are starting to see
great uplift here.

00:32:47.150 --> 00:32:48.740
Game developers
are seeing install

00:32:48.740 --> 00:32:51.110
conversions increased
by up to 20%

00:32:51.110 --> 00:32:52.880
with a great instant experience.

00:32:52.880 --> 00:32:55.760
And this is particularly
useful for paid apps and games

00:32:55.760 --> 00:32:59.960
where now you can enable try
before you buy functionality.

00:32:59.960 --> 00:33:02.060
As a result of
the success, we've

00:33:02.060 --> 00:33:05.030
expanded the footprint of
instant across the store

00:33:05.030 --> 00:33:07.870
by syndicating the Try
Now button everywhere.

00:33:07.870 --> 00:33:10.010
And with the advent
of the app bundle

00:33:10.010 --> 00:33:11.900
and improved
integration into Unity,

00:33:11.900 --> 00:33:13.670
adopting instant is
easier than ever.

00:33:17.620 --> 00:33:21.490
Lastly, we've been
focused on monetization.

00:33:21.490 --> 00:33:24.380
In the last year, we expanded
our international footprint,

00:33:24.380 --> 00:33:26.450
especially in emerging markets.

00:33:26.450 --> 00:33:29.400
We added seller support
to 31 new markets.

00:33:29.400 --> 00:33:32.180
We expanded our wallet
program to cover 14 countries,

00:33:32.180 --> 00:33:35.210
and we added 20 new direct
care, building partnerships

00:33:35.210 --> 00:33:36.710
our direct carrier
billing footprint

00:33:36.710 --> 00:33:39.920
alone reaches over 1.3
billion devices in the fleet,

00:33:39.920 --> 00:33:43.465
